{"color": "green", "emoji": "\ud83d\udcac", "event_type": "Agent Message", "message": "Plan: 1. Add a dedicated planning-heuristics module in the backend with explicit assumptions and pure calculations for word count, runtime, chapter size, and suggestion logic. 2. Reuse the same heuristics model in the story-setup UI via...", "raw_event": {"item": {"id": "item_34", "text": "Plan:\n1. Add a dedicated planning-heuristics module in the backend with explicit assumptions and pure calculations for word count, runtime, chapter size, and suggestion logic.\n2. Reuse the same heuristics model in the story-setup UI via a small frontend helper so the form can show approximate ranges and optional \u201capply suggestion\u201d actions without overwriting what the user already set.\n3. Add targeted backend and frontend tests, then run type-safe frontend validation, backend tests, and browser QA against the Docker Compose app before writing the required summary file and checkpoint commit(s).", "type": "agent_message"}, "type": "item.completed"}, "task_display_context": {"event_number": 67, "prompt_index": 52, "prompt_name": "51 \u2014 Correlation Heuristics for Word Count, Runtime, and Chapters", "prompt_total": 100}, "timestap": "2026-04-02T01:53:02-07:00"}
