                         <div className=\"summary-pa...\">\n                              <div>\n                              <dl>\n                              <InlineHelp title=\"Word count...\" tone=\"info\">\n                                <aside className=\"inline-hel...\">\n                                  <strong>\n>                                 <p className=\"inline-help__body\">\n>                                   <div className=\"story-setup-stage__heuristic\">\n                              ...\n          ...\n\n[browser:error] <%s> cannot contain a nested %s.\nSee this log for the ancestor stack trace. p <div>\nSaved failure screenshot to /workspace/.artifacts/webapp-qa/failure.png\nError: Expected text not found: \"2400 words in 14 minutes implies about 171 words per minute, which sits outside the usual bedtime range of 120-160.\"\nCurrent page text:\nSkip to main content\n\nBEDTIME STORY STUDIO\n\nStoryteller\nSessions\nWorkspace\n\nResume existing stories or open a session workspace when you are ready to continue.\n\nCONNECTION\n\nBackend reachability\nLast checked 9:08 AM.\nOnline\nCheck again\n\nThe app shell is connected to FastAPI through the Vite development proxy.\n\nHello from FastAPI!\n\nSESSION WORKSPACE\n\nPrompt 49 Beat Editor QA\n\nChat and stage-driven workflow controls now share one persistent surface, with the left lane reserved for conversation and the right canvas reserved for structured editing.\n\nCurrent stage\nComposition\nSave status\nSaved Apr 2, 8:43 AM\nSession ID\n8155bbd7-2de7-4d4c-a961-d35485225ed0\nLive updates\nIdle\n\nSet VITE_SESSION_EVENTS_WS_URL to enable live updates.\n\nNeeds refresh\nReturn home\nLive feed idle\nIn progress\n\nThe workspace is running from the durable snapshot only. Configure the websocket endpoint to start session-scoped live updates.\n\nChat lane\n\nMessages, action echoes, and redirect notes stay visible beside the structured workflow.\n\nLive feed idle\n\nReady for notes, approvals, and