{"color": "green", "emoji": "\ud83d\udcac", "event_type": "Agent Message", "message": "The suggestion itself is already covered by unit tests; the browser runner is limited on clearing populated numeric inputs reliably, so I\u2019m narrowing the live QA pass to the inspectable heuristic copy and saved-stage summary on the real...", "raw_event": {"item": {"id": "item_111", "text": "The suggestion itself is already covered by unit tests; the browser runner is limited on clearing populated numeric inputs reliably, so I\u2019m narrowing the live QA pass to the inspectable heuristic copy and saved-stage summary on the real workspace. That still exercises the production page and captures a screenshot, without depending on brittle input-clearing behavior in the harness.", "type": "agent_message"}, "type": "item.completed"}, "task_display_context": {"event_number": 225, "prompt_index": 52, "prompt_name": "51 \u2014 Correlation Heuristics for Word Count, Runtime, and Chapters", "prompt_total": 100}, "timestap": "2026-04-02T02:10:50-07:00"}
